					<description><![CDATA[<p>Norm Ai Raises $120 Million to Advance AI-Native Legal Services Norm Ai has raised $120 million in a Series C funding round led by Khosla Ventures. Blackstone, Bain Capital Ventures,</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/norm-ai-raises-120-million-series-c/" data-wpel-link="internal">Norm Ai Raises $120 Million Series C to Expand AI Legal Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><b>Norm Ai Raises $120 Million to Advance AI-Native Legal Services</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Ai has raised $120 million in a Series C funding round led by Khosla Ventures. Blackstone, Bain Capital Ventures, Craft Ventures, Coatue, Vanguard, New York Life, TIAA, Fenwick LLP and several industry leaders also joined the round.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The latest financing brings Norm Ai&#8217;s total funding to more than $260 million since the company launched less than three years ago. The business plans to use the capital to recruit more talent, expand legal practice areas and strengthen its supervisory AI agents for regulated industries.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Ai combines artificial intelligence engineers with experienced lawyers to build AI systems that embed legal reasoning into automated <a href="https://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english/workflow" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external">workflows.</a> The company also operates Norm Law, an AI-native law firm that delivers legal services using AI agents supervised by senior attorneys.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Founder and chief executive officer John Nay said the company&#8217;s goal is to build an interface between artificial intelligence and legal systems, helping organisations align AI with established legal standards.</span></p>
<h2><b>AI Agents Support Legal Work and Compliance</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Ai focuses on high-stakes industries where legal compliance remains critical. Its technology enables organisations to deploy AI agents that understand regulations while supporting internal legal teams and business operations.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company&#8217;s AI systems also supervise other AI agents working in regulated environments. This additional oversight helps organisations monitor automated decision-making and reduce compliance risks as AI adoption increases.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Unlike traditional legal firms that charge clients based on billable hours, Norm Law prices many of its services according to outcomes. This model better aligns its incentives with client success while allowing efficiency gains from artificial intelligence to benefit customers directly.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Law has also assembled an experienced legal team led by former senior partners and executives from several international law firms. Human lawyers continue supervising and refining the AI systems used to deliver legal services.</span></p>
<h2><b>Enterprise Demand Drives Platform Growth<br />
</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_203390" style="width: 1322px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203390" class="size-full wp-image-203390" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/a-futuristic-neon-lit-poster-showcases-a_25-_3Zq6UHS-PC-YPS2Upg_E2CSC-vjR56bCkmAd8zXng_cover.png" alt="A neon futuristic visual showing AI-powered legal systems used by financial institutions with strong governance and compliance frameworks." width="1312" height="736" /><p id="caption-attachment-203390" class="wp-caption-text">Norm Ai gains traction among major institutions as demand grows for trusted AI-driven legal and compliance solutions. Source: Created by Ventureburn</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Ai says organisations representing more than $30 trillion in combined assets under management already use its technology. Customers deploy the platform to automate legal workflows while improving governance across regulated operations.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company has also attracted attention from major financial institutions seeking to integrate AI into complex legal and compliance processes. Investors believe institutional trust will become a defining factor as artificial intelligence expands into highly regulated industries.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Samir Kaul, Managing Director at Khosla Ventures, said widespread adoption of AI in regulated sectors depends on building trusted systems capable of meeting legal and governance requirements. He added that Norm Ai has developed a credible approach for delivering AI-native legal services at enterprise scale.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/cvc-raises-3-billion-catalyst-iii/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">CVC Raises €3B for Catalyst III to Expand Mid-Market Investments</span></a></p>
<h2><b>Legal AI Market Continues to Expand</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Artificial intelligence is reshaping legal services as organisations seek faster document review, compliance monitoring and contract analysis. Startups across the sector continue developing specialised AI tools that reduce repetitive work.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Norm Ai has positioned itself differently by combining legal software with an AI-native law firm operating on the same technology platform. The company believes this integrated approach provides continuous feedback that strengthens both its AI products and legal services.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">As businesses increasingly adopt artificial intelligence across legal and financial operations, Norm Ai aims to become a key provider of trusted AI governance solutions for enterprise customers.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To stay updated on crypto venture capital funding and market trends, visit our </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/category/news/venture-capital/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital news section</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> for more insights.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/norm-ai-raises-120-million-series-c/" data-wpel-link="internal">Norm Ai Raises $120 Million Series C to Expand AI Legal Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
