<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Registering on a crypto exchange in the UAE is a fairly simple process. For this example, we would be using Binance, a licensed and regulated exchange with the best P2P crypto platform. To register on Binance, do the following. </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Account Setup</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Go to the official Binance website. Click on Sign Up and open your account using your email or mobile number. Create a username and password.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-195671 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/1-Binance.jpg" alt="Step-by-Step: How to Register on a UAE Crypto Exchange" width="1857" height="986" /></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Providing Personal Information</span></h3>
